---
description: 
alwaysApply: true
---

Commit format: <type>(<scope>): <subject>

Types allowed: feat, fix, refactor, perf, style, docs, test, chore, ci, revert
- Use English
- Present tense, imperative
- No capital letter at start
- No dot at the end
- Max 72 chars for subject line
- One commit = one purpose
- Use refactor only when behavior does not change
- Scope is optional (e.g., "feat:" or "feat(auth):")
